<br>
Run another test 3d, this time have Origen put protect, guard and intercept on Malady (45th level runemaster on Pendragon) and give it your best shot. Try and kill Malady at all. Then when you're done, try and kill Origen again 1v1 WITHOUT running through his body, i.e. you must turn away from him as if his body was solid....and he will shield stun you and chop you to pieces. It won't happen. <br>
